flowchart LR
  browser[Browser submission] --> api[POST /api/preflight-plan]
  api --> analyzer[Server-only deterministic AST analyzer]
  analyzer --> deterministic[Deterministic boundary fixtures]
  deterministic --> provider{Gemini available?}
  provider -->|yes: metadata only| gemini[Gemini structured proposal]
  provider -->|no or failure| fallback[Deterministic fallback]
  gemini --> validation[Zod proposal validation]
  validation --> materialize[Trusted requirement and fixture materialization]
  materialize --> merge[Stable merge and cap]
  fallback --> merge
  merge --> runplan[RunPlanSchema v1]
  runplan --> display[Planned, not executed]
